page_title: 'Quickstart: Use Azure OpenAI Service with the Java SDK to generate images'
page_description: Walkthrough on how to get started with Azure OpenAI and make your first image generation call with the Java SDK.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free* The current version of the Java Development Kit (JDK)* The Gradle build tool, or another dependency manager.- An Azure OpenAI resource created in the East US region. For more information, see Create a resource and deploy a model with Azure OpenAI.
